    "Note that each of these approaches helped to reduce the computational complexity and parameter quantity of the model.",
    "Particularly, compared to the baseline with MSF, the baseline with CBAM achieved 1.9% higher mAP.",
    "The examination of the experimental data indicates that the CBAM significantly improves the feature extraction capabilities of the model's backbone when building the CRA block.",
